query:
SELECT 
  ce.id,
  c.name as course_name,
  ce.traineeCount,
  ce.paidAmount,
  ce.enrollmentDate
FROM courseEnrollments ce
LEFT JOIN courses c ON ce.courseId = c.id
WHERE ce.enrollmentDate >= '2025-02-01' AND ce.enrollmentDate <= '2025-02-28'
ORDER BY ce.enrollmentDate;
